      {
        "type": "element",
        "tagName": "document-steps",
        "properties": {},
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "h3",
            "properties": {
              "id": "doc-content-准备基础配置和独立-secret"
            },
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "准备基础配置和独立 Secret"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "p",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "复制 "
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": ".env.example"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": " 为 "
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": ".env"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "，至少配置数据库、Better Auth、外部 HTTPS Origin 和助理运行模式。动态模型控制面还需要两组独立数据库角色、一个 AES-256-GCM 主密钥和一个 Web/Agent 内部控制凭据。"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "pre",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {
                  "className": [
                    "language-text"
                  ]
                },
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "install -d -m 700 .secrets\numask 077\nopenssl rand -hex 32 > .secrets/agent_control_migrator_database_password\nopenssl rand -hex 32 > .secrets/agent_control_database_password\nopenssl rand -hex 32 > .secrets/model_config_encryption_key\nopenssl rand -hex 32 > .secrets/agent_config_control_key\nchmod 600 .secrets/*\n"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "p",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "控制角色密码使用上面的十六进制值时，可直接生成对应 DSN 文件："
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "pre",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {
                  "className": [
                    "language-text"
                  ]
                },
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "control_migrator_password=$(tr -d '\\n' < .secrets/agent_control_migrator_database_password)\ncontrol_runtime_password=$(tr -d '\\n' < .secrets/agent_control_database_password)\nprintf 'postgresql+psycopg_async://ai_agent_control_migrator:%s@db:5432/ai_agent_platform\\n' \"$control_migrator_password\" > .secrets/agent_control_migrator_database_url\nprintf 'postgresql+psycopg_async://ai_agent_control:%s@db:5432/ai_agent_platform\\n' \"$control_runtime_password\" > .secrets/agent_control_database_url\nunset control_migrator_password control_runtime_password\nchmod 600 .secrets/agent_control_*_database_url\n"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "p",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "两条 DSN 分别使用 "
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "ai_agent_control_migrator"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": " 和 "
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "ai_agent_control"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "，密码必须与对应密码文件一致。"
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "MODEL_CONFIG_ENCRYPTION_KEY"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "、"
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "AGENT_CONFIG_CONTROL_KEY"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "、"
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "OS_SECURITY_KEY"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "、认证密钥和会话密钥不得复用。"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "h3",
            "properties": {
              "id": "doc-content-初始化平台agentos-和模型控制数据库"
            },
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "初始化平台、AgentOS 和模型控制数据库"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "pre",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {
                  "className": [
                    "language-text"
                  ]
                },
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "docker compose build migrate agent-migrate agent-control-migrate agent web backup\ndocker compose up -d --wait db\ndocker compose run --rm migrate\ndocker compose run --rm agno-bootstrap\ndocker compose run --rm agent-control-bootstrap\ndocker compose run --rm --no-deps agent-migrate\ndocker compose run --rm --no-deps agent-control-migrate\n"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "p",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "agent-control-bootstrap"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": " 只创建最小权限角色；"
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "agent-control-migrate"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": " 使用 migrator DSN 创建并校验 "
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {},
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "value": "agent_control"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": " schema。迁移失败时不要启动 Agent，也不要把 migrator DSN 挂载给常驻 Agent 或 Web。"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "h3",
            "properties": {
              "id": "doc-content-选择部署级开关"
            },
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "选择部署级开关"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "p",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "value": "要启用码多多和后台模型控制面，设置："
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tagName": "pre",
            "properties": {},
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tagName": "code",
                "properties": {
                  "className": [
                    "language-text"
